1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,509
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,979
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,159
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,399
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,729
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,319
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,609
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,059
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,289
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,709
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,199
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,749
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,169
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,999
=No Way! My Bro is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,160
=Episode 10=

19
00:01:15,770 --> 00:01:17,370
Xiaoyao Pavilion

20
00:01:17,380 --> 00:01:19,530
used to send reports every day.

21
00:01:20,250 --> 00:01:21,609
Why have they suddenly gone silent?

22
00:01:21,610 --> 00:01:22,610
Your Majesty.

23
00:01:23,130 --> 00:01:23,769
Your Majesty.

24
00:01:23,770 --> 00:01:25,129
Something terrible has happened.

25
00:01:25,130 --> 00:01:26,099
What is it?

26
00:01:26,100 --> 00:01:26,969
Official Gu...

27
00:01:26,970 --> 00:01:27,890
What happened to Gu Bei?

28
00:01:28,210 --> 00:01:28,819
It's not him.

29
00:01:28,820 --> 00:01:29,960
It's Xiaoyao Pavilion.

30
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:31,980
Xiaoyao Pavilion has had
hardly any customers lately.

31
00:01:32,130 --> 00:01:34,730
Official Gu has been
looking worried all day.

32
00:01:34,940 --> 00:01:36,450
Don't make such a fuss.

33
00:01:36,690 --> 00:01:38,060
Calm down and tell me what happened.

34
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:39,579
Your Majesty,

35
00:01:39,580 --> 00:01:41,179
I went to deliver Official Gu's salary,

36
00:01:41,180 --> 00:01:42,849
as Your Majesty ordered.

37
00:01:42,850 --> 00:01:44,200
When I got there, I found out

38
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:46,440
a new establishment
had opened across the street.

39
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,530
It's called Zuixian House.

40
00:01:47,770 --> 00:01:48,899
It's just another tavern.

41
00:01:48,900 --> 00:01:49,819
It's nothing.

42
00:01:49,820 --> 00:01:52,899
But it was packed from opening day.

43
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:55,450
It stole all
Xiaoyao Pavilion's customers.

44
00:01:55,850 --> 00:01:57,179
How is that possible?

45
00:01:57,180 --> 00:01:59,890
I've experienced Xiaoyao Pavilion myself.

46
00:02:00,050 --> 00:02:00,810
Where's Gu Bei?

47
00:02:00,850 --> 00:02:01,890
What's he doing?

48
00:02:01,900 --> 00:02:02,579
I heard

49
00:02:02,580 --> 00:02:04,579
he's meeting
Princesses Xiao Ling and Hulv

50
00:02:04,580 --> 00:02:05,730
for ideas.

51
00:02:06,130 --> 00:02:07,179
At this rate,

52
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:08,259
I fear

53
00:02:08,260 --> 00:02:09,209
Xiaoyao Pavilion

54
00:02:09,210 --> 00:02:10,769
will go out of business.

55
00:02:10,770 --> 00:02:12,890
Such a big problem,

56
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,700
and he didn't come to me?

57
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:20,450
Prepare the carriage. I'll see for myself.

58
00:02:20,610 --> 00:02:21,330
Yes, Your Majesty.

59
00:02:22,030 --> 00:02:23,310
Welcome!

60
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,189
Welcome!

61
00:02:24,190 --> 00:02:25,190
This way, please.

62
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:32,320
(Zuixian House, The Best Massage Parlor)

63
00:02:34,650 --> 00:02:37,050
I opened Xiaoyao Pavilion
so I could live an easy life.

64
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:39,420
Now even that's become a competition.

65
00:02:40,300 --> 00:02:43,419
You leave me no choice
but to show no mercy.

66
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:45,179
So how would you fight back?

67
00:02:45,180 --> 00:02:46,859
Hulv scalded their money tree,

68
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:49,260
and Xiao Ling had a fortune teller
make curse talismans.

69
00:02:49,740 --> 00:02:50,979
None of it worked.

70
00:02:50,980 --> 00:02:52,210
What a load of superstition.

71
00:02:52,980 --> 00:02:53,980
Don't do that.

72
00:02:58,330 --> 00:02:59,660
Look! Look at them.

73
00:02:59,740 --> 00:03:01,259
(Zuixian House)
The Best Massage Parlor.

74
00:03:01,260 --> 00:03:02,260
Do they have no shame?

75
00:03:02,330 --> 00:03:03,259
Before I opened,

76
00:03:03,260 --> 00:03:05,419
these people didn't even know
what massage was.

77
00:03:05,420 --> 00:03:07,210
How dare they claim they're the best?

78
00:03:07,980 --> 00:03:09,980
I'm smashing their place.

79
00:03:10,450 --> 00:03:11,649
Calm down.

80
00:03:11,650 --> 00:03:13,100
Everyone's watching.

81
00:03:13,180 --> 00:03:14,579
If you trash their shop,

82
00:03:14,580 --> 00:03:17,300
they'll call you a sore loser.

83
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:19,300
A sore loser?

84
00:03:19,980 --> 00:03:21,139
Me?

85
00:03:21,140 --> 00:03:22,610
What a joke.

86
00:03:23,020 --> 00:03:25,080
You're not just the owner anymore.

87
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,720
You're also Commander
of the Imperial Guards.

88
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:27,739
If you smash their sign

89
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:28,579
and the word gets out,

90
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:31,730
people will say we're abusing our power.

91
00:03:32,930 --> 00:03:34,770
Aren't we already?

92
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:39,420
Fair point.

93
00:03:39,490 --> 00:03:40,100
But

94
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:42,210
we have to be subtle.

95
00:03:44,050 --> 00:03:45,170
What's your plan?

96
00:03:49,171 --> 00:03:50,260
Relax.

97
00:03:50,980 --> 00:03:51,899
I'll show you

98
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:53,210
how an emperor

99
00:03:54,020 --> 00:03:56,660
handles things.

100
00:04:12,310 --> 00:04:13,079
Bravo!

101
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:13,439
(Workaholic)

102
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:13,959
(Just Chill)

103
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,199
(Workaholic, Just Chill)

104
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:18,040
(Work Hard, Get Rich)

105
00:04:19,650 --> 00:04:21,699
Why are we wearing sunglasses?

106
00:04:21,700 --> 00:04:22,730
And the fake beard?

107
00:04:22,850 --> 00:04:24,499
I'm the owner of Xiaoyao Pavilion.

108
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:26,679
If I'm spending money at
my competitor's place, it's embarrassing.

109
00:04:26,679 --> 00:04:27,860
I have to disguise myself.

110
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:30,340
(Work Hard, Get Rich)
No one noticed you before.

111
00:04:30,380 --> 00:04:32,020
Now you stand out.

112
00:04:32,290 --> 00:04:33,420
What do you know?

113
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:34,860
Welcome, sirs.

114
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:35,980
First time here?

115
00:04:36,970 --> 00:04:38,019
Give us

116
00:04:38,020 --> 00:04:39,370
your best service.

117
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:40,529
Certainly.

118
00:04:40,530 --> 00:04:41,570
One moment.

119
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,200
(Zuixian House)

120
00:04:49,210 --> 00:04:50,899
So this is

121
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:52,340
your emperor's strategy?

122
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:53,780
Money

123
00:04:54,060 --> 00:04:55,660
solves everything.

124
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:58,459
Didn't you say the treasury was empty?

125
00:04:58,460 --> 00:04:59,130
It is.

126
00:04:59,650 --> 00:05:01,220
That's why I'm spending your money.

127
00:05:05,900 --> 00:05:07,690
- Hello! Welcome!
- Hello! Welcome!

128
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:17,100
The decor,

129
00:05:17,330 --> 00:05:18,409
the services,

130
00:05:18,410 --> 00:05:19,409
even the uniforms

131
00:05:19,410 --> 00:05:21,340
are exactly like mine.

132
00:05:21,410 --> 00:05:23,169
This isn't plagiarism.

133
00:05:23,170 --> 00:05:24,690
It's copy and paste.

134
00:05:24,850 --> 00:05:28,100
Please enjoy
our complimentary fruit and liquor.

135
00:05:32,730 --> 00:05:35,490
Copying the massages is one thing,

136
00:05:36,530 --> 00:05:37,420
but look at the tags

137
00:05:37,770 --> 00:05:39,020
and free fruit.

138
00:05:39,170 --> 00:05:39,690
Um.

139
00:05:40,140 --> 00:05:41,250
They're way ahead.

140
00:05:45,530 --> 00:05:46,370
This way upstairs.

141
00:05:47,170 --> 00:05:49,579
Xiao. Something's up on the second floor.

142
00:05:49,580 --> 00:05:50,540
Let's go check it out.

143
00:05:50,700 --> 00:05:51,420
Hold on.

144
00:05:52,380 --> 00:05:54,690
Did you notice his tag was blue?

145
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,289
Please.

146
00:05:57,290 --> 00:05:58,490
Ours are yellow.

147
00:05:58,700 --> 00:05:59,660
They won't let us up.

148
00:06:08,380 --> 00:06:09,250
Watch this.

149
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,130
Let's go.

150
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:26,939
This way.

151
00:06:26,940 --> 00:06:27,459
Let's go.

152
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:28,100
Let's go.

153
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,840
(Get Rich)

154
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:46,720
(Get Rich)

155
00:06:50,090 --> 00:06:50,980
What are you doing?

156
00:06:55,330 --> 00:06:57,020
You two look new.

157
00:06:57,290 --> 00:06:58,370
Which floor?

158
00:06:59,770 --> 00:07:00,570
Second floor.

159
00:07:00,850 --> 00:07:02,809
Last two digits? Let me check.

160
00:07:02,810 --> 00:07:03,560
(Name, Member ID)

161
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:07,240
(63, 78)

162
00:07:08,290 --> 00:07:10,860
That's just like Didi.
[*A ride-hailing app]

163
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:12,300
Could the owner

164
00:07:12,460 --> 00:07:13,690
be a time traveler too?

165
00:07:17,530 --> 00:07:18,860
I want to see your boss.

166
00:07:21,940 --> 00:07:22,730
What?

167
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:24,340
Not enough?

168
00:07:29,730 --> 00:07:32,420
That's my money.

169
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:36,660
Enough now?

170
00:07:37,730 --> 00:07:38,860
I hear

171
00:07:50,650 --> 00:07:52,250
someone asked for me.

172
00:07:53,460 --> 00:07:54,810
Are you the boss here?

173
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:55,719
Lady boss?

174
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,209
(Yan Qiu, owner of Zuixian House)

175
00:07:57,210 --> 00:07:58,860
I'm Yan Qiu.

176
00:07:58,940 --> 00:08:00,570
I'm the owner of Zuixian House.

177
00:08:00,620 --> 00:08:02,379
You asked for me.

178
00:08:02,380 --> 00:08:03,810
How may I help?

179
00:08:05,090 --> 00:08:05,730
Test her.

180
00:08:07,460 --> 00:08:08,810
We've spent quite a lot here.

181
00:08:09,460 --> 00:08:11,460
Can we become

182
00:08:12,020 --> 00:08:14,340
VIPs?

183
00:08:23,090 --> 00:08:25,420
Unlike Xiaoyao Pavilion,

184
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:27,019
we treat

185
00:08:27,020 --> 00:08:28,570
every guest equally.

186
00:08:28,900 --> 00:08:30,050
Miss,

187
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:32,380
running a business is fine,

188
00:08:33,170 --> 00:08:35,570
but copying Xiaoyao Pavilion,

189
00:08:36,260 --> 00:08:39,570
don't you think
that's a little shameless?

190
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:44,420
(Not a single giveaway.)

191
00:08:45,050 --> 00:08:46,780
(Could she really be one of us?)

192
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:48,289
If everyone is equal,

193
00:08:48,290 --> 00:08:50,420
why can't we enter those private rooms?

194
00:08:52,380 --> 00:08:53,660
Unfortunately,

195
00:08:53,740 --> 00:08:56,260
they're all booked today.

196
00:08:56,570 --> 00:08:57,739
Gentlemen,

197
00:08:57,740 --> 00:08:59,570
why not make a reservation

198
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:00,900
for tomorrow?

199
00:09:03,770 --> 00:09:04,660
Very well.

200
00:09:05,380 --> 00:09:06,620
It's a deal.

201
00:09:06,690 --> 00:09:07,660
We'll be back

202
00:09:07,900 --> 00:09:08,780
tomorrow.

203
00:09:11,650 --> 00:09:12,660
Let's go.

204
00:09:13,450 --> 00:09:14,219
Quick.

205
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:15,380
This is embarrassing.

206
00:09:18,020 --> 00:09:19,260
Mr. Gu.

207
00:09:19,690 --> 00:09:21,740
Since you're so fond of this place,

208
00:09:21,810 --> 00:09:23,170
do come often.

209
00:09:32,650 --> 00:09:34,509
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

210
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:36,889
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

211
00:09:36,890 --> 00:09:42,329
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

212
00:09:42,330 --> 00:09:46,709
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

213
00:09:46,710 --> 00:09:49,119
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

214
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:51,659
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

215
00:09:51,660 --> 00:09:57,329
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

216
00:09:57,330 --> 00:10:02,890
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

217
00:10:07,180 --> 00:10:09,240
♪Funny moments never stop♪

218
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:12,050
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

219
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:16,419
♪Yet through every up and down♪

220
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:18,390
♪We create miracles♪

221
00:10:18,690 --> 00:10:21,150
♪From naive youths♪

222
00:10:21,410 --> 00:10:23,889
♪To legendary heroes♪

223
00:10:23,890 --> 00:10:25,839
♪This journey♪

224
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:29,849
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

225
00:10:29,850 --> 00:10:32,400
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

226
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:37,740
♪Let's create♪

227
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:47,700
♪A legend of our own♪
